  "texts": [
    "The developed model is highly significant in sectors such as rehabilitation, where the forecasting movement intent can tune the treatment interventions and observe the progress.Practical implications: The developed human motion intention prediction process can be applicable in distinct practical applications including rehabilitation robotics, fall prevention, prosthetic control, and augmented reality assistance.",
    "By forecasting the movement of an individual utilizing the developed model, the robotic systems can offer timely support during the physical therapy exercises, adapting to the individual's requirements in real-time and highly enhancing the recovery solutions.",
    "Moreover, for elderly people, at risk of falls, the developed model can forecast the potential falls that can provide timely interventions to mitigate the injuries.",
    "Thus, the developed human motion intention prediction process helps in the clinical sector effectively.Implications of the findings: The developed human motion intention prediction process achieves relatively superior solutions in terms of distinct measures such as BA, f1-Score, FOR, MK, sensitivity, and so on.",
